  KnownBugs
=============

- Blockop should support multiple endianesses (currently only big-endian)
- Cursor misplacement in image (F4)
- Help / features / configuration PgDn

- Cancel search should not say "not found"
- window resize + cursor positioning problems
- going to lines with ofs % 16 !=0 (+clipboard)

- some problems when run on non-x86 systems... (Sparc bus error e.g.)
- doesn't compile on Solaris (curses problems) and MacOS X (X_textmode problems)

